OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781384335
OL,3,CNHS faces 'triple whammy' during
OL,4,Cresident doctor walkout
OL,6,FThe NHS is facing a "triple whammy of
OL,7,Fpressure" as the latest strike by
OL,8,Fresident doctors is set to coincide
OL,9,Fwith a heatwave and the World Cup,
OL,10,Fhealth officials have said.
OL,12,FResident doctors in England from the
OL,13,FBritish Medical Association (BMA) are
OL,14,Fset to stage a four-day walk out from
OL,15,F7am on Monday ` the 16th round of
OL,16,Fstrike action since 2023.
OL,18,FThe walk out will end on Friday June
OL,19,F19 at 6.59am.
OL,26,@nD@UOUoD@IO]
