OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781384335
OL,3,CNHS faces 'triple whammy' during
OL,4,Cresident doctor walkout
OL,6,FNHS officials have urged the public to
OL,7,Fcome forward as usual but are
OL,8,Fexpecting a rise in need linked to a
OL,9,Fpredicted heatwave and activity linked
OL,10,Fto England's first World Cup game on
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,13,FIt is expected that pubs and bars will
OL,14,Fbe busy as the Three Lions take on
OL,15,FCroatia at 9pm UK time.
OL,17,FMeanwhile the Met Office forecasts
OL,18,Fsuggest that temperatures will be
OL,19,F"generally above normal" between
OL,20,FTuesday and Thursday.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
