OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781384335
OL,3,CNHS faces 'triple whammy' during
OL,4,Cresident doctor walkout
OL,6,FNHS England said that patients should
OL,7,Fcontinue to attend all planned
OL,8,Fappointments unless they are
OL,9,Fspecifically contacted directly to
OL,10,Frearrange them.
OL,12,FAnd anyone with urgent or emergency
OL,13,Fneed should seek care in the normal
OL,14,Fway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
