OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781384335
OL,3,CNHS faces 'triple whammy' during
OL,4,Cresident doctor walkout
OL,6,FProfessor Frankie Swords, national
OL,7,Fmedical director at NHS England, said:
OL,8,F"The NHS remains open as usual during
OL,9,Fthis period of industrial action, with
OL,10,Fstaff across the NHS doing everything
OL,11,Fthey can to keep patients safe and
OL,12,Fminimise disruption to services.
OL,14,F"With temperatures set to rise again
OL,15,Fthis week and the World Cup kicking
OL,16,Foff ` it will be triple whammy of
OL,17,Fpressure, but staff will pull together
OL,18,Fas they always do, to keep the show on
OL,19,Fthe road and ensure people continue to
OL,20,Freceive the care they need.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781384335
OL,3,CNHS faces 'triple whammy' during
OL,4,Cresident doctor walkout
OL,6,F"It is important during any heatwave,
OL,7,Fthat people try to stay cool, stay out
OL,8,Fof the sun, and stay hydrated during
OL,9,Fthe hottest hours, and seek help when
OL,10,Fthey need it, especially those who are
OL,11,Fvulnerable including the very young,
OL,12,Felderly and those with underlying
OL,13,Fhealth conditions.
OL,15,F"Please come forward for care as
OL,16,Fnormal, call 999 or attend A&E in an
OL,17,Femergency, and use 111 online first
OL,18,Ffor urgent but non-life-threatening
OL,19,Fsupport."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
