OL,3,CNHS faces 'triple whammy' during
OL,4,Cresident doctor walkout
OL,6,FWhen the strike was announced in May,
OL,7,FBMA officials said that Health
OL,8,FSecretary James Murray "made clear" he
OL,9,Fwill not increase the offer to
OL,10,Fresident doctors.
OL,12,FThe union said that more strike dates
OL,13,Fin July could also be announced.
OL,15,FSpeaking at the NHS ConfedExpo
OL,16,Fconference in Manchester, Health
OL,17,FSecretary James Murray said: "I was
OL,18,Freally disappointed that the resident
OL,19,Fdoctors are going to strike next week.
OL,26,@pD@XOUpD@cO]yD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781384335
OL,3,CNHS faces 'triple whammy' during
OL,4,Cresident doctor walkout
OL,6,F"I met them within my first couple of
OL,7,Fweeks in office and I explained to
OL,8,Fthem my position, which is that there
OL,9,Fis a really good offer on the table
OL,10,Fwhen it comes to pay: a 28.9% increase
OL,11,Fover the last three years, 4.9%
OL,12,Fincrease this year, which rises to
OL,13,F7.1% for some of the lowest-paid
OL,14,Fresident doctors.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781384335
OL,3,CNHS faces 'triple whammy' during
OL,4,Cresident doctor walkout
OL,6,F"We cannot go further on pay, but when
OL,7,Fit comes to other aspects of the deal,
OL,8,Fwhen it comes to job opportunities, to
OL,9,Fterms and conditions, training
OL,10,Foptions, that is where I want to work
OL,11,Fwith them to strengthen the deal as
OL,12,Fmuch as possible.
OL,14,F"And we have been having some good
OL,15,Fconversations about that.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781384335
OL,3,CNHS faces 'triple whammy' during
OL,4,Cresident doctor walkout
OL,6,F"I'm disappointed that, despite having
OL,7,Fthose conversations about how to
OL,8,Fimprove other aspects of the deal,
OL,9,Fthat the strikes are still set to go
OL,10,Fahead, and I would urge them, even
OL,11,Ftoday, to continue that conversation
OL,12,Fwith us about the other aspects of the
OL,13,Fdeal, other than pay, and make that as
OL,14,Fstrong as possible for their members,
OL,15,Fbecause that would be for the benefit
OL,16,Fof resident doctors and all of us as
OL,17,Fpatients."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781384335
OL,3,CNHS faces 'triple whammy' during
OL,4,Cresident doctor walkout
OL,6,FSir Ciaran Devane, chief executive of
OL,7,Fthe NHS Alliance, said: "Local NHS
OL,8,Fleaders have become all-too familiar
OL,9,Fwith dealing with industrial action
OL,10,Fstemming from this long and damaging
OL,11,Fdispute.
OL,13,F"Yet again, every effort will be made
OL,14,Fduring next week's walkout to minimise
OL,15,Fdisruption to patients, despite
OL,16,Fpotential additional pressures as a
OL,17,Fresult of the weather and the football.
OL,19,F"But there will be some knock-on
OL,20,Fdelays to care which will be hugely
OL,21,Ffrustrating for those affected.
OL,26,@nD@IrpoD@YOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781384335
OL,3,CNHS faces 'triple whammy' during
OL,4,Cresident doctor walkout
OL,6,F"And for every stoppage there is a
OL,7,Fvery significant hit to NHS finances.
OL,9,F"Even at this late stage we urge both
OL,10,Fsides, the Government and the BMA, to
OL,11,Fget together and resolve this dispute
OL,12,Fonce and for all."
OL,14,FThe BMA has been approached for
OL,15,Fcomment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
